<h2><br/>
Frontiers in Complex Systems</h2>
<p>Maxi San Miguel</p>
<p>In this paper I intend to give an answer to three entangled questions: What is a Complex System?, What are present research challenges in Complex Systems?, and What is the purpose of the new journal Frontiers in Complex Systems?</p>
<p>Read the full article at: <a href="https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fcpxs.2023.1080801/full" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">www.frontiersin.org</a></p>
